    <!-- Goals Section -->
    <section id="goals" class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6">Goals</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            <li>Promote Entrepreneurship: Initiate, encourage, and support entrepreneurial initiatives that drive economic growth and create job opportunities within the diaspora, hosting communities, and the region.</li>
            <li>Drive Social Transformation: Initiate and support programs that promote social change, community empowerment, and development among the diaspora and the region.</li>
            <li>Enhance Education and Skills: Advocate for and support educational initiatives that enhance knowledge and skills development among the diaspora and the region.</li>
            <li>Advance Technology: Promote and facilitate the adoption of technology to drive innovation and development within the diaspora and the region.</li>
            <li>Cultivate Leadership: Train and develop responsible leaders who can guide their communities towards sustainable development and unity.</li>
        </ul>
